 Gibbs distribution. Our approach demonstrates the\nfeasibility of using quantum annealers for implementing generative models, and\nit provides a suitable framework for benchmarking these quantum technologies on\nmachine-learning-related tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 19:30:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 May 2017 16:23:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 17:30:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 20:34:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-29"}
