 analysis is\nalso applied to rigid scale covariance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2016 08:56:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2017 10:47:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
