e pulse) that occurs in a normally-stable regime. Our results test the\napproximate analytical solutions with an unprecedented degree of accuracy and\nprovide new insights into dissipative-soliton dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2016 09:44:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 08:29:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2018 17:23:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-29"}
